---
// CustomerSegmentBlock — verbatim copy from readonlyrest.com per v5 §3.2.
// Used on homepage and /regulated.
---

<section class="customer-segments">
  <span class="section-eyebrow">Beshu Tech, since 2017</span>
  <h2>Trusted by remarkable organisations</h2>
  <p class="segment-lede">
    Hundreds of organisations trust Beshu Tech. Customers that make us
    <strong>extra proud</strong>:
  </p>
  <ul class="segment-list">
    <li><span class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">📈</span> <strong>2× in the S&amp;P 500 top 5</strong></li>
    <li><span class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">🧸</span> <strong>2× charities protecting children</strong></li>
    <li><span class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚛️</span> <strong>3× nuclear research institutions</strong></li>
    <li><span class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">🇪🇺</span> <strong>2× European Union institutions</strong></li>
    <li><span class="segment-icon" aria-hidden="true">👮‍♀️</span> <strong>Various government institutions</strong></li>
  </ul>
  <p class="segment-disclaimer">
    These customer references reflect Beshu Tech's customer base for
    <a href="https://readonlyrest.com">ReadonlyREST</a>. They do not
    imply any endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation with
    DeltaGlider.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .segment-lede {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--ink-strong);
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }

  .segment-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    max-width: 38rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 600px) {
    .segment-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .segment-list li {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .segment-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .segment-disclaimer {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    max-width: var(--measure);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
</style>
